{"tid":116263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【請選擇】正妹理想身材 - 正皮左邊 負皮右邊","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T15:21:26.000Z","uid":52127,"like":338,"dislike":584,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8de913f6b00d67f3a39ea988080bfec348fb3bb","tid":116263,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NAUWP2Kl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNAUWP2Kl.jpg&h=80b83c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男女生眼中的「好身材」，標準真的大不同？<br />\n日本最近一則推特貼文爆紅，網友ぽんた分享一張兩位比基尼正妹同框的照片，左邊的女生標註「女生的理想體型」、右邊則是「男生理想的女生體型」，只見照片中左邊女生身材纖細、而右邊女孩較豐腴，引發網友熱烈討論，難道男生都比較愛「肉肉的女生」嗎？<br />\n這篇推文有超過2萬8千人轉推、3萬7千人按讚，引起相當大迴響，左邊右邊各有擁護者，有網友說「我會很誠實說，我選右」「肉肉的抱起來才舒服」「兩個都不錯，但內行的應該會選右」「我的理想&rarr;左」「左，可以掌握感覺比較好」，但也有網友貪心的說「左擁右抱」「左的臉+右的身」「我...我都可以」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170211/1053838/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170211%2F1053838%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1xOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=7e36c5f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170211/1053838/</a>"},{"pid":"95f073242734810294b8fb9804269ead1a60d900","tid":116263,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:06:59.000Z","msg":"一定右"},{"pid":"c0b1215e904a0bbd1a9f5e79cc1c40444d14a31c","tid":116263,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29855e8bdb2790a9c09052db4da4b430a6f8fcc7","tid":116263,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c55327084e0571e14d4e4b83cbf00b813408ac0","tid":116263,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"呃負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />